PREFERRED_DEFINITION: The interviewer asks the respondent for his/her date of birth in MM/DD/YYYY format. If the respondent does not know his/her date of birth the interviewer asks an alternative question to determine his/her age. NOTE:  The current age of the respondent can be calculated, given the date of the interview.
ORIGIN: NHANES: National Health and Nutrition Examination Survey, 2005-2006
